1.00	Karmapa_International_Buddhist_Institute	Karmapa International Buddhist Institute	Karmapa International Buddhist Institute (also known as K.I.B.I. or KIBI) is a school of higher learning based on the great treatises of Buddhism. Founded by Shamar Rinpoche, K.I.B.I. aims at furthering wisdom and compassion based on the Karma Kagyu tradition of Tibetan Buddhism.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/76/KIBI.jpg/220px-KIBI.jpg
